{"tid":1979204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[向對家偷師]時刻幫自己洗腦，凡係屌手足唔屌對家嘅全部都講緊大話","createTime":"2020-04-19T09:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T12:39:03.000Z","uid":48234,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26472d8b28c5b5e26cf51c7e0b79685b85100bb8","tid":1979204,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:06:52.000Z","msg":"要比對家更齊心一致，抗爭先會有希望<br />\n各有各做，可以提出意見<br />\n針對手足嚟屌，從來唔屌對家嘅，必須當佢全部講緊大話<br />\n<br />\n呢樣嘢，就係各位手足輸俾對家嘅其中一樣嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1284a29e1ddfa80333f62c29f41e424dab1f41","tid":1979204,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:09:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8410ed33692038187b8c5e94e435638ba46344a","tid":1979204,"uid":48234,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔駛諗太多嘢<br />\n直接洗腦，對家講大話<br />\n搞掂!</span></span>"},{"pid":"f69c783ae8b189885cea2245a2d32746bb3f8842","tid":1979204,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:53:48.000Z","msg":"屌=五毛 搞撚掂晒<br />\n話之你屌我屈毛又好關我撚事"},{"pid":"d73bad2426391c5d3bf9caf8e8c90a594f5a46b7","tid":1979204,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f69c783ae8b189885cea2245a2d32746bb3f8842","tid":1979204,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T09:53:48.000Z","msg":"屌=五毛 搞撚掂晒<br />\n話之你屌我屈毛又好關我撚事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:13:05.000Z","msg":"最高境界，連五唔五毛都廢事理<br />\n對手足不利 = 講大話<br />\n其他啲就另外再諗吓信唔信<br />\n既可激勵手足士氣，亦可將對家嘅攻擊化為烏有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95661b443dbb26854b85fd5a98db472325c0e535","tid":1979204,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T10:14:48.000Z","msg":"就算係老鳳唔小心講錯對手足不利嘅嘢<br />\n一樣可以當講大話/假膠處理<img src